headline: Regions Bank Named 2025 Gallup Exceptional Workplace Award Winner
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., March 26, 2025--Regions Bank is proud to announce it has received the 2025 Gallup Exceptional Workplace Award (GEWA) for employee engagement. This award recognizes the most engaged workplace cultures in the world. This is the 11th year Regions has been recognized by Gallup.
